---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Curfew & Caretaker Policy | Jyoti Girls PG"
  description="Review the curfew timings, caretaker supervision, and accountability measures followed at Jyoti Girls PG near Osmanpura."
>

  <section style="padding: 60px 0 40px; background: var(--color-bg-base);">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Girls PG near Osmanpura</span>
      <h1 class="section-heading">Curfew &amp; Caretaker Policy</h1>
      <p class="section-lead">Discipline is the backbone of Jyoti Girls PG. Our clearly defined curfew rules keep residents safe while maintaining parent confidence.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background: var(--color-bg-white);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-heading">Daily Curfew Timings</h2>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:20px;">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Weekday Schedule</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">Residents return by 9:00 PM after classes. Attendance is taken at 9:30 PM, followed by study hour until lights-out at 11:00 PM.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Weekend Flexibility</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">Curfew extends to 10:00 PM on Saturdays for cultural events or mock tests, with prior parent approval.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Special Permissions</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">Outings for family functions or coaching workshops are granted after written consent and ID verification of the escort.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background: var(--color-bg-subtle);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-heading">Caretaker Supervision</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:20px;max-width:600px;">
        <li style="color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin-bottom:10px;">Female warden resides on-site with two assistants covering 24x7 shifts.</li>
        <li style="color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin-bottom:10px;">Entry and exit are logged in a digital register shared with parents every evening.</li>
        <li style="color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin-bottom:10px;">Night patrols cover each floor at fixed intervals to ensure lights-out discipline.</li>
        <li style="color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin-bottom:10px;">Guardians receive SMS alerts for delayed arrivals or unscheduled exits.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background: var(--color-bg-white);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-heading">Emergency &amp; Escalation Process</h2>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:20px;margin-bottom:40px;">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Medical Support</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">In case of illness, the caretaker accompanies the resident to nearby Osmanpura clinics and updates the guardian instantly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Fire &amp; Safety Drills</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">Quarterly drills train residents on safe evacuation routes and assembly points.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Parent Helpline</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">Dedicated helpline numbers remain active day and night to assist families or handle special requests.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <button class="btn-primary" data-modal="availability">Book a policy briefing</button>
        <a href="https://wa.me/919922333305?text=Hello%20Jyoti%20Girls%20PG%2C%20please%20share%20your%20curfew%20policy." class="btn-whatsapp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Request the rulebook</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
